data.description: MOVE IN READY. This four-side brick home has recently been updated with Carpet, Paint, Fixtures, Foundation, Professionally installed French Drain, Trane AC, Electric panel, Gas meter, blinds, dishwasher, vent-hood, Dishwasher and Gas Range.... Enjoy your backyard with mature trees, raised large storage building with hardy board siding. Oversize Master, walk-in closets, built-ins and ceiling fans in every room! Located only 2 min. from I-10, close to Schools, Hospital & Shopping.
